{
  "texts": [
    "We consistently observe that our multi-task framework outperforms LLMs.",
    "For example, on the SWMH dataset, the multi-task RoBERTa's F1 score exceeds that of the highestperforming LLM, MentaLLaMA-chat-7B, by approximately 13 percentage points.",
    "In the PsySym dataset, the multi-task RoBERTa's F1 score of 83.3% showcases its effectiveness, even surpassing the 0-shot performance of ChatGPT.",
    "Comparing Table 4 and 5, we observe that LLMs in general did not outperform light weighted BERT models.",
    "This research represents a pioneering effort in contrasting single-task and multi-task modeling approaches within the domain of mental health analysis."
  ]
}